<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62c5f979-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s3804"><num value="3804">§ 3804.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out this chapter. Funds provided under this chapter are to be considered nonreimbursable.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62c5f97a-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/302/s5">Pub. L. 103–302, § 5</ref>, <date date="1994-08-23">Aug. 23, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1563">108 Stat. 1563</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
